From Bob Blackshaw Subject Re Remember those names come election In anwar Anwar Mohammed writes I said In article Peter Nelson writes Besides there's no case that can be made for US military involvement there that doesn't apply equally well to say Liberia Angola or it appears with the Khmer Rouge's new campaign Non whites don't count might say Kuwaitis are non Ooops I forgot Kuwaitis are oil rich loaded with petro dollars etc so they don't let's not forget Somalia which is about as far from white as it Not according to reports I have It seems that the Somalis think of our African American Marines in less than complimentary terms using gestures that signify a word I refuse to Seems that even when you try to help people they still insult That's two in a row care to try for more REB